<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA624_04_IH_0001</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema624_04.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema624_04_ih_0001">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1_deep_green">
          <span class="empty_box nemo"></span>
          <span lang="y">안에 알맞은 수를 써넣으세요.</span>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center align_start">
          <div class="img_area">
            <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA624_04_IH/0001_bg.png" alt="" />
            <div class="text_area">
              <div class="text_row">
                <span lang="y">2:5를 비율로 나타내면</span>
                <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap" data-hint-position="up">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="(2)/(5)" class="w_80"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span lang="y">, 10:25를 비율로 나타내면</span>
                <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap" data-hint-position="up">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="(10)/(25)" class="w_large" data-answer-multi='{"values": ["(10)/(25)","(2)/(5)"]}' data-multi-hint="y"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span lang="y">입니다.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text_row">
                <span lang="y">두 비의 비율이 같으므로 비례식을 세우면 2:</span>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="5"></math-field>
                </div>
                =
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="10"></math-field>
                </div>
                :
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="25"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span lang="y">입니다.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y" class="flex align_center gap_0">
                    2 : 5를 비율로 나타내면&nbsp;
                    <span class="fraction_box trans_y_center">
                      <span>2</span>
                      <span>5</span> </span
                    >, 10 : 25를 비율로 나타내면&nbsp;

                    <span class="fraction_box">
                      <span>10</span>
                      <span>25</span>
                    </span>

                    <span class="bracket flex align_center gap_0">
                      <span class="bracket-l"></span>

                      <span class="eq-middle">=</span>
                      <span class="fraction_box">
                        <span>2</span>
                        <span>5</span>
                      </span>

                      <span class="bracket-r"></span>
                    </span>

                    입니다.
                  </p>
                  <p>두 비의 비율이 같으므로 비례식을 세우면 2 : 5 = 10 : 25입니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
